title: 2016 Week 16 review
itunes:title: 2016 Week 16 review
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling, and Gregg Rosenthal – recap the action in Week 16 which included the Browns finally coming up with their first win of the season, plus a couple key injuries that have major playoff implications.
